The first series has the same problem. Report from @laurenobell:

I am trying to "complete" this item in Figgy. It is the first series of the one I had an issue with last week (which was the second series of the collection). I'm receiving the same error as last time. (bib ID: 9919685413506421)
- Figgy item: https://figgy.princeton.edu/catalog/21e392d3-4bc3-4d6d-bea7-2228d623b455
- Figgy error: https://figgy.princeton.edu/concern/scanned_resources/21e392d3-4bc3-4d6d-bea7-2228d623b455

We should fix the new instance, and think about ways to make sure we don't inherit arks for resources which are in Figgy but already have that ARK maybe?

Document the use case.
